{"tid":1637313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國通輯犯張五常 : 「學校沒教具重量中国文化科」","createTime":"2019-10-08T02:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T06:26:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"711f3df4f371693e263a719e59401050861ab5af","tid":1637313,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"反修例風波持續多月未平息，示威活動不斷。著名經濟學家張五常上月在深圳大學演講亦有提及香港情況，他認為目前香港的青年上街，主要是因為他們的學校沒有教少許重量的關於中國文化的科目，又指不懂國家的文化，不會對國家有歸屬感。<br />\n<br />\n    &quot;我認為對中國文化缺乏認識是香港收不到錢的學生上街的主要原因。不懂國家的文化不會對國家有歸屬感。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n張五常指出，為什麼昔日的英國統治香港，那時的中小學教中國的古文、詩詞，遠比今天為多。今天在內地的小學生，差不多全部可以背得出起碼幾十首中國的詩詞與古文。無數的小學生研習中國的書法。<br />\n<br />\n    &quot;「愛國」一詞我不知何解。我這個老人家在地球上活了八十多年，從來不覺得有哪個國家可愛。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n   &quot; 我有無數舊學生今天是香港的中學老師，為了要理解香港學子的上街行為，我問他們香港中學的「通識科」是教什麼。他們一律說是教廢物。為什麼納稅人的錢要花在廢物上呢？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n張五常又指，2012年11月發表了《國民教育與藝術文化》，建議香港的中小學著重於教中國的文化。如果當時香港接納了他的建議，今天那裡的學生不會跑到街上去。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2467127/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%BC%B5%E4%BA%94%E5%B8%B8%E8%AB%87%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%20%20%E3%80%8C%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E6%B2%92%E6%95%99%E5%85%B7%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%A7%91%E3%80%8D?mtc=20033</code></pre>"},{"pid":"224c5c15a749049bfd091d8333730b4a8942ec93","tid":1637313,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"要教幾多磅先夠？"},{"pid":"4430975dff15f0a21f9d5c6df7c01522b17de82f","tid":1637313,"uid":70392,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"on9 最破壞中國文化既就係中共 越熟讀中國文化只會越反共 你咪嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad59450bbf00ea1b1eab55fd30b0dad94bd31eab","tid":1637313,"uid":317795,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:02:32.000Z","msg":"ON9 我就係讀中史先知代代皇帝都係玩愚民政策，同埋明朝之後再冇中國"},{"pid":"9bcc91f14b10d9789e896c7a943c5a28292b8f90","tid":1637313,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:06:35.000Z","msg":"重量<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbe677d0124b737ba7cfbdd99ff3b5234c2be57","tid":1637313,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:18:31.000Z","msg":"喺美國愛中國，<br />\n依D愛國情慾太高了。"},{"pid":"0f034157df86ad79d889e70e0857ca3df815cec5","tid":1637313,"uid":32983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:19:31.000Z","msg":"交稅啦張五常垃圾"},{"pid":"f37681abf2b7ac0d2be9c9dfd25898896fff487e","tid":1637313,"uid":129848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:23:06.000Z","msg":"做美國公民交稅咁基本都未做到就唔好指指點點人地教育制度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78d42be8e117721b2110cdd1a1c647c7027ef3b","tid":1637313,"uid":314132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"不如講白啲，開個再教育營去洗你腦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講到咁撚好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bbe2c7c2189fcf3d1114f2cdd8c9962e6e8a86","tid":1637313,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ef87d40b6d605ce2d95066fbb1d2a592c28a3b","tid":1637313,"uid":305518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:05:37.000Z","msg":"張五常李天命😞"},{"pid":"c39f0247c6a99f6904900d09edae7f349c0c4a44","tid":1637313,"uid":311004,"like":3,"dislike":0,"s